Package: CarefullyCausal
Type: Package
Title: Provides estimates, assumptions and diagnostics for fixed-exposure causal analyses
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Maurice", "Korf", email = "m.korf@erasmusmc.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Jeremy", "Labrecque", email = "j.labrecque@erasmusmc.nl", role = "aut"))
Description: This package provides the estimand, estimators, assumptions and diagnostics
      for causal analyses in a fixed-exposure setting using observational data.
      It supports: outcome regression, IPTW, S-and-T-standardization and TMLE.
License: `use_mit_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
