    survey (>= 4.1.1),
    stats (>= 4.2.2),
    cobalt (>= 4.5.1),
    boot (>= 1.3.28),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.1),
    ggridges (>= 0.5.4)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://github.com/mauricekorf/CarefullyCausal
